item.title: Tanya Morgan really is a rap group, not a woman
item.description: DJ Chizzad was full in effect in NYC for CMJ 06 checking out the hottest hip hop up and comings, and little did i realize a taste of cincinnati was in that rat race to be fresh to death. No question was Tanya Morgan ahead of the pack with Illyas Don Will and Von P spittin the flow. I had the chance to talk to them during the scion party at this penthouse midtown manhattan. We went out on the balcony to talk to them. the picture of them is on my profile.
